.SH NAME
tag remove \- Remove tags from a book
.SH SYNOPSIS
alexandria> tag remove
.SH DESCRIPTION
.TP
Prompts for a book reference (ID, ISBN, title, or author) and comma-separated tags.
.TP
Removes matching tags from the selected book.
.SH EXAMPLES
